{"id": 1827, "genre": 1001, "title": "网上买东西，你一般用什么凑单？", "description": "你都用哪些东西来填满你购物车的缝隙？（题图来自：Wikimedia Commons）", "record_count": 1934, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170801100307pPVH3wYTSJk7KbMI.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-02T03:00:18Z", "options": [{"id": 226819, "content": "人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1043839}, {"id": 226820, "content": "书。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 601802}, {"id": 226821, "content": "订外面满减差一元不到，买十个辣椒包凑单", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 849766}, {"id": 228101, "content": "零食", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 707312}, {"id": 226822, "content": "放着不会坏的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 849032}, {"id": 226823, "content": "手纸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1067236}, {"id": 226824, "content": "一般要凑单，就不买了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262489}, {"id": 226825, "content": "宁可给邮费，也不买不需要的东西回来闲置而凑单。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1075446}, {"id": 227082, "content": "书", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1096118}, {"id": 226827, "content": "真的需要，不必凑单，邮费值得；不是必需品，凑单那一刻，决定不买。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076224}, {"id": 226829, "content": "可以囤货的生活必需品&零食", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 705899}, {"id": 226830, "content": "本来想买10元，凑着凑着凑成了100元～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1095275}, {"id": 226831, "content": "尽量避免凑单，凑单的时候比买想买的东西的选择更纠结，如果不得不的情况，那就零食吃的来凑，哈哈?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1079810}, {"id": 227343, "content": "文具吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1096810}, {"id": 227599, "content": "买的是什么，就多买一点凑单", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 444860}, {"id": 228623, "content": "生活必需品，像洗衣液、卫生纸什么的刚需用品", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893693}, {"id": 226320, "content": "凑单区里的新零食、新洗涤剂什么的", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 226832, "content": "哈哈哈", "image": "img/option/option/20170803103744PyFaUMlfrscwjON3.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1095546}, {"id": 226321, "content": "不看凑单区，已经购买的商品多买一件", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 226322, "content": "买书的话，会用杂志凑单", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 226834, "content": "自己可以用的，凑单比较便宜。能省则省。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040473}, {"id": 226323, "content": "像小红书这样的，就用易耗品凑单，润唇膏，化妆棉之类", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 226835, "content": "有的用习惯凑单，有的习惯性的不会凑单！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 787171}, {"id": 226836, "content": "基本都送，用书签这类小东西补", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1095222}, {"id": 231701, "content": "米饭 馒头 醋 辣椒的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1114972}, {"id": 227095, "content": "纸巾卫生巾，水果", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1096161}, {"id": 227863, "content": "VIP免邮", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098733}, {"id": 226840, "content": "不网购", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130912}, {"id": 226841, "content": "尽量凑到包邮……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1095567}, {"id": 226842, "content": "小食品", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1061136}, {"id": 226843, "content": "从来没凑过单", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1090065}, {"id": 227101, "content": "找个跟邮费价格差不多的东西买。如果差很多就算了，或者找人拼单喽", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1095958}, {"id": 232221, "content": "生活日用品", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1075131}, {"id": 227616, "content": "不会凑单，零钱会收集起来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098172}, {"id": 226597, "content": "化妆棉", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094611}, {"id": 226853, "content": "纸巾", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902265}, {"id": 226598, "content": "宁可花邮费也不凑单 凑单比邮费贵 还竟是没用的 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 336, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094715}, {"id": 226599, "content": "江浙沪包邮，从不凑单", "image": null, "praise_count": 175, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970782}, {"id": 227879, "content": "零食吧，新鲜一点的，不买太多还是吃得完的～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098555}, {"id": 226600, "content": "就拍邮费链接来凑！", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1055639}, {"id": 227112, "content": "需要凑单的就不买", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1031607}, {"id": 226601, "content": "没有意义的调查。完全取决于店铺的主营业务。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 95, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879838}, {"id": 226602, "content": "点外卖经常加个饮料满足减付条件", "image": null, "praise_count": 268, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1051333}, {"id": 226603, "content": "食物", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094726}, {"id": 227371, "content": "一般不花冤枉钱买不需要的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1090839}, {"id": 226604, "content": "有一次买缝被针 凑单凑齐了一套针线盒：2个顶针 穿针器 剪刀 划线粉饼 针插", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651076}, {"id": 226860, "content": "点个冰淇淋 饮料啥的凑一个减负", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1083827}, {"id": 226605, "content": "决不！", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1087715}, {"id": 226606, "content": "凑单？no", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 997563}, {"id": 226607, "content": "用书....", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719655}]}